  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b92\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A one-and-a-half-year-old child died after falling into a bucket of water in Yali",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna. A one-and-a-half-year-old child fell into a bucket of water and died in Ponnalai West.",
        "This afternoon, while the child's mother was cooking, the child fell into a bucket of water in the yard and died.",
        "After finishing cooking, the mother went looking for the child but did not find the child. When the mother and the neighbors searched for the child, it was observed that the child had fallen into a bucket of water.",
        "After this, the neighbors rescued the child and took him to Moolai Hospital, but the doctors said that the child had already died.",
        "In this case, the dead body of the child is currently kept at the Moolai Cooperative Hospital, while the Vattukkottai police are conducting further investigations."
      ],
